  "2192070": {
    "name": "Traildown: Downhill Mountain Biking",
    "steam_appid": 2192070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192070/extras/3f89ca60e3ef7814c8a33b3253e750c5.avif?t=1764761979\" width=616 height=100 /></span>Traildown: Downhill Mountain Biking is all about giving the player the maximum passion from the ride. Go as fast as you can, just on edge, and try to achieve the best time. Achieve medals and compare yourself to the others on the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192070/extras/9b7875705c914e8c78d51d69cecf59fc.avif?t=1764761979\" width=616 height=100 /></span>The game consists of a campaign with tens of unique levels. The estimated gameplay time is about 4 hours. Achieving perfect times and climbing to the top of the leaderboards takes 10/100s of hours and very big balls. Can you make it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192070/extras/7df1ef5336158c9cebfe806f5d753b36.avif?t=1764761979\" width=616 height=100 /></span>You are able to fully customize your bike with any color and a huge variety of patterns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192070/extras/815cf9450387819d657d3cdff24cdc87.avif?t=1764761979\" width=616 height=100 /></span>I am a Ph.D. student indie developer. I have been developing the fre2play franchise &quot;Engine Evolution&quot; for 6 years, and now I have decided that I would like to try a different challenge. I always enjoy riding the bike down the hill fast, and I am trying to capture it as best as possible in this upcoming game.</p>",
